# Cloudflare Pages — per-path Cache-Control overrides.
#
# Goal: stop serving stale HTML after a deploy without breaking
# normal caching for hashed assets (which are immutable anyway).
#
# - HTML: no-cache forces Chrome / CF edge to revalidate every load.
#   The HTML is tiny so this is cheap; the assets it imports use
#   content-hashed filenames so old HTML can never reference new
#   asset URLs, which is the whole reason the stale-HTML bug bites.
# - _astro/* (content-hashed): immutable + 1y. Filename hash flips
#   when content flips, so a cached asset is correct by construction.
# - service worker (sw.js): never cache. Stale SW = stale everything.
# - PWA manifests: short cache so app-name / icon updates land soon.
# - Static images served by the user (favicons etc): default 1h.
#
# Third-party CDNs (jsdelivr/strudel, unpkg/hydra, fonts.googleapis,
# etc.) are unaffected — these headers only cover voidstar.sh's own
# files. Their cache behavior is dictated by their own headers.

# Security headers (all paths). Deliberately minimal — a full CSP would break
# the CDN-loaded Strudel/Hydra/MediaPipe imports and the inline boot scripts,
# so we only set frame-ancestors (clickjacking) plus the cheap hardening
# headers. NO COOP/COEP: nothing uses SharedArrayBuffer, and cross-origin
# isolation would break those same CDN imports. The setlist/mind apps hold
# Google Drive OAuth tokens in localStorage, so framing protection matters.
/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self'
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(self), microphone=(self), geolocation=(self), midi=(self), interest-cohort=()

/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/_astro/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/sw.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/*.webmanifest
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300

/favicon.svg
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600

/icon-*.png
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
